        "details": "<div class=\"value-sans\">\n<p class=\" value-medium\">Fed up with the amount of plastic bottles they had to carry around their home, they decided to do something about it \n\n</p>\n<span class=\"gray-text value-medium\">They both knew the power and joy in natural cleaning, so they started experimenting with formulas in their garage. It's there that they conjured up Counter Clean for all around the home, and Bathroom Bliss for tricky water stains.\n</span>\n</div>",
        "man_details_1": "We manufacture Purdy &amp; Figg concentrates in the UK, where we are subject to stringent health regulations.",
        "man_details_2": "Every Purdy &amp; Figg refill is produced and packaged at our factory in Hertfordshire, where our dedicated team keep our customers’ safety in mind every step of the way"
